I'm going to listen to you now

00:08:29.830 --> 00:08:31.070 align:middle line:90%
and respect it.

00:08:31.070 --> 00:08:34.179 align:middle line:84%
So part of that was
bringing the science in

00:08:34.179 --> 00:08:38.470 align:middle line:84%
