respectability in the society.

00:08:38.470 --> 00:08:41.110 align:middle line:84%
Now that that's
happened, it's really,

00:08:41.110 --> 00:08:43.929 align:middle line:84%
what about the personal
journey that you have to take?

00:08:43.929 --> 00:08:46.120 align:middle line:90%
That's really much more--

00:08:46.120 --> 00:08:47.320 align:middle line:90%
that's the next step.

00:08:47.320 --> 00:08:49.330 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: That's kind of what
I'm talking about with you,

00:08:49.330 --> 00:08:50.140 align:middle line:90%
yes.

00:08:50.140 --> 00:08:53.020 align:middle line:84%
And here we are at a time
where the whole COVID

00:08:53.020 --> 00:08:57.670 align:middle line:84%
phenomena has swept through
the countries of the world.

00:08:57.670 --> 00:09:00.970 align:middle line:84%
People are left
with new questions,

00:09:00.970 --> 00:09:03.760 align:middle line:84%
ideally, left with
questions about,

00:09:03.760 --> 00:09:07.870 align:middle line:84%
was this former way of
living really working for me?

00:09:07.870 --> 00:09:11.350 align:middle line:84%
Is that what I had intended
to manifest for a life?

00:09:11.350 --> 00:09:15.040 align:middle line:84%
Or was it simply running
on autopilot and programs?

00:09:15.040 --> 00:09:19.300 align:middle line:84%
And it seems like this is a good
time to go back and revisit,

00:09:19.300 --> 00:09:22.450 align:middle line:84%
go deeper this time,
and look at our creation

00:09:22.450 --> 00:09:24.790 align:middle line:84%
and what we're offering
of ourselves in the world.

00:09:24.790 --> 00:09:27.790 align:middle line:84%
So it sounds like this
could be pretty good timing

00:09:27.790 --> 00:09:31.390 align:middle line:84%
for a world that should be
more reflective at this moment

00:09:31.390 --> 00:09:32.680 align:middle line:90%
than it was in the past.

00:09:32.680 --> 00:09:34.880 align:middle line:84%
>>ARNTZ: Well, and it's
definitely going to happen.

00:09:34.880 --> 00:09:37.215 align:middle line:84%
I mean, basically, you
think about a retreat.

00:09:37.215 --> 00:09:38.590 align:middle line:84%
If you go into
spiritual retreat,

00:09:38.590 --> 00:09:40.255 align:middle line:90%
it's that you leave your life.

00:09:40.255 --> 00:09:42.130 align:middle line:84%
You'll leave it all
behind, your normal life,

00:09:42.130 --> 00:09:43.135 align:middle line:90%
and you go off somewhere.

00:09:43.135 --> 00:09:43.935 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:09:43.935 --> 00:09:45.430 align:middle line:84%
>>ARNTZ: Well,
everyone-- this is

00:09:45.430 --> 00:09:47.560 align:middle line:84%
the first time in the
history of the planet where

00:09:47.560 --> 00:09:49.090 align:middle line:84%
the whole planet's
been put on retreat.

00:09:49.090 --> 00:09:49.840 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:09:49.840 --> 00:09:50.590 align:middle line:90%
>>ARNTZ: Think about it.

00:09:50.590 --> 00:09:50.890 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah.

00:09:50.890 --> 00:09:51.690 align:middle line:90%
No, it's amazing.

00:09:51.690 --> 00:09:53.590 align:middle line:84%
>>ARNTZ: It's a
completely new phenomena.

00:09:53.590 --> 00:09:56.290 align:middle line:84%
And so part of in the
collective unconscious, everyone

00:09:56.290 --> 00:09:58.070 align:middle line:90%
is experiencing the same thing.

00:09:58.070 --> 00:10:02.410 align:middle line:84%
So it's a planetary
initiation, essentially,

00:10:02.410 --> 00:10:03.550 align:middle line:90%
is what's going to happen.

00:10:03.550 --> 00:10:08.215 align:middle line:84%
And the thing with initiations
is it can go one of two ways.

00:10:08.215 --> 00:10:09.938 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes, depending on us.

00:10:09.938 --> 00:10:10.980 align:middle line:90%
>>ARNTZ: Depending on us.

00:10:10.980 --> 00:10:15.250 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And it's interesting
because it promises to--

00:10:15.250 --> 00:10:17.560 align:middle line:84%
at this point, it's already
happening-- collapse

00:10:17.560 --> 00:10:20.920 align:middle line:84%
a lot of the old structures,
including there's

00:10:20.920 --> 00:10:25.030 align:middle line:84%
going to be a lot
of ramifications

00:10:25.030 --> 00:10:29.200 align:middle line:84%
in our economic world
around us, and that's

00:10:29.200 --> 00:10:31.720 align:middle line:84%
going to affect us on
deeply personal levels.

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:34.780 align:middle line:84%
But again, that
world was created

00:10:34.780 --> 00:10:40.120 align:middle line:84%
in such an unthoughtful way,
in a way that exploits so many

00:10:40.120 --> 00:10:44.470 align:middle line:84%
and serves so few, that we
fight and think, oh, no.

00:10:44.470 --> 00:10:47.420 align:middle line:84%
We don't want the stock
markets of the world to crash.

00:10:47.420 --> 00:10:50.470 align:middle line:84%
We don't want our, you know, to
have our GDP drop and all that.

00:10:50.470 --> 00:10:54.100 align:middle line:84%
But then you stop and look
at it and say, OK, we're

00:10:54.100 --> 00:10:56.270 align:middle line:84%
going to have to rip the
Band-Aid off at some point.

00:10:56.270 --> 00:10:58.840 align:middle line:84%
Where do we get down to
an organic way of living,

00:10:58.840 --> 00:11:01.690 align:middle line:90%
an organic connected economy?

00:11:01.690 --> 00:11:03.550 align:middle line:90%
When do we let it die?

00:11:03.550 --> 00:11:06.883 align:middle line:84%
Just let it do a
freefall to an extent.

00:11:06.883 --> 00:11:09.050 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we still have to
eat and live and have jobs.

00:11:09.050 --> 00:11:14.030 align:middle line:84%
But I think if we even have
that internal intention,

00:11:14.030 --> 00:11:16.820 align:middle line:84%
we can contend with what's
going to be happening

00:11:16.820 --> 00:11:18.530 align:middle line:84%
over the next couple
of years, I think,

00:11:18.530 --> 00:11:20.810 align:middle line:84%
better and create something
more beautiful out of it.

00:11:20.810 --> 00:11:22.102 align:middle line:90%
What are your thoughts on that?

00:11:22.102 --> 00:11:25.850 align:middle line:84%
>>ARNTZ: Well, I think
it's going to make people

00:11:25.850 --> 00:11:27.980 align:middle line:90%
reflect on their core values.

00:11:27.980 --> 00:11:32.120 align:middle line:84%
What is really important, and
what gives you a good life?

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:34.630 align:middle line:84%
And I was watching
Governor Cuomo talk.

00:11:34.630 --> 00:11:36.710 align:middle line:84%
And he goes, you
know, everyone, I just

00:11:36.710 --> 00:11:39.170 align:middle line:84%
had a two-hour conversation
with my daughter.

00:11:39.170 --> 00:11:41.930 align:middle line:84%
I've never had a two-hour
conversation with my daughter.

00:11:41.930 --> 00:11:44.150 align:middle line:84%
I can't tell you what
that meant to me.

00:11:44.150 --> 00:11:46.550 align:middle line:84%
And so you start saying,
well, all this stuff

00:11:46.550 --> 00:11:51.040 align:middle line:84%
what we were doing to give
ourselves a great life,

00:11:51.040 --> 00:11:52.190 align:middle line:90%
it didn't really do it.

00:11:52.190 --> 00:11:54.100 align:middle line:90%
But what is, what is important?

00:11:54.100 --> 00:11:55.562 align:middle line:84%
It's those moments
that you have.

00:11:55.562 --> 00:11:57.520 align:middle line:84%
It's the moments when
you connect with someone.

00:11:57.520 --> 00:12:00.880 align:middle line:84%
It's the moments where
you get an inspiration

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:03.430 align:middle line:84%
or you read something, or you
learn the piece and, you know?

00:12:03.430 --> 00:12:08.410 align:middle line:84%
It's not necessarily having
the new granite countertops

00:12:08.410 --> 00:12:09.503 align:middle line:90%
for the kitchen.

00:12:09.503 --> 00:12:10.420 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Absolutely.

00:12:10.420 --> 00:12:14.440 align:middle line:84%
>>ARNTZ: So I think that the
people are going to-- on this

00:12:14.440 --> 00:12:15.400 align:middle line:90%
retreat--

00:12:15.400 --> 00:12:16.600 align:middle line:90%
are going to look at that.

00:12:16.600 --> 00:12:20.110 align:middle line:84%
Now, the trouble with this is,
and this is the suffering part

00:12:20.110 --> 00:12:23.590 align:middle line:84%
of it, is whenever you take
stuff away from people, all

00:12:23.590 --> 00:12:26.710 align:middle line:84%
the stuff that we've created
to make our life what

00:12:26.710 --> 00:12:28.600 align:middle line:90%
it is, you take it all away.

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:30.160 align:middle line:90%
Think about a four-year-old.

00:12:30.160 --> 00:12:32.380 align:middle line:84%
What happens when suddenly,
you take away the thing

00:12:32.380 --> 00:12:33.355 align:middle line:90%
they're playing.

00:12:33.355 --> 00:12:34.570 align:middle line:90%
Ah.

00:12:34.570 --> 00:12:35.710 align:middle line:84%
So there's going to be
an emotional reaction.

00:12:35.710 --> 00:12:36.580 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --freaking out.

00:12:36.580 --> 00:12:36.770 align:middle line:90%
Sure.

00:12:36.770 --> 00:12:38.395 align:middle line:84%
>>ARNTZ: People are
going to freak out.

00:12:38.395 --> 00:12:41.320 align:middle line:84%
So the important thing
is, I think, to let people

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:43.480 align:middle line:84%
know, OK, you're going
to be freaking out,

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:44.800 align:middle line:84%
and your friends are
going to be freaking out,

00:12:44.800 --> 00:12:46.270 align:middle line:84%
and people are
going to be angry.

00:12:46.270 --> 00:12:48.835 align:middle line:84%
But you have to realize it's
the process we're going through.

00:12:48.835 --> 00:12:49.635 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:12:49.635 --> 00:12:51.430 align:middle line:84%
And keep those core
values in mind.

00:12:51.430 --> 00:12:52.810 align:middle line:84%
It's the same
thing in California

00:12:52.810 --> 00:12:57.280 align:middle line:84%
where I live which was not
terribly affected by all of it.

00:12:57.280 --> 00:12:59.920 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people are
living a rural life there.

00:12:59.920 --> 00:13:02.050 align:middle line:84%
And one thing that
happened from--

00:13:02.050 --> 00:13:04.150 align:middle line:84%
