gardening centers.

00:13:04.150 --> 00:13:08.440 align:middle line:84%
Those things look like
Black Friday at a mall.

00:13:08.440 --> 00:13:11.140 align:middle line:84%
All of the centers
were packed with nearly

00:13:11.140 --> 00:13:13.960 align:middle line:84%
