00:14:49.590 --> 00:14:51.540 align:middle line:84%
I know people now
in the software.

00:14:51.540 --> 00:14:54.100 align:middle line:84%
And they, you know, 2
o'clock Sunday morning, they

00:14:54.100 --> 00:14:54.900 align:middle line:90%
