00:14:59.130 --> 00:15:00.150 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: That's
no way to live.

00:15:00.150 --> 00:15:00.900 align:middle line:90%
>>ARNTZ: It's no way to live.

00:15:00.900 --> 00:15:01.983 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: No way to live.

00:15:01.983 --> 00:15:02.915 align:middle line:90%
So we're in agreement.

00:15:02.915 --> 00:15:05.040 align:middle line:84%
I think everyone watching
