I'm sorry.

00:15:05.390 --> 00:15:06.240 align:middle line:90%
What were you going to say?

00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:08.550 align:middle line:84%
>>ARNTZ: I was going to say,
you know, even according--

00:15:08.550 --> 00:15:09.675 align:middle line:90%
