>>ARNTZ: Come on everyone,
you can take a day off.

00:15:14.833 --> 00:15:15.870 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:15:15.870 --> 00:15:18.203 align:middle line:84%
OK, so now, we're going
to talk about what

