right?

00:15:31.350 --> 00:15:33.420 align:middle line:90%
And so now comes the suffering.

00:15:33.420 --> 00:15:36.321 align:middle line:84%
I think your book's
right on time.

00:15:36.321 --> 00:15:39.600 align:middle line:84%
>>ARNTZ: "How to Suffer
in 10 Easy Steps."

00:15:39.600 --> 00:15:40.560 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: OK.

00:15:40.560 --> 00:15:42.170 align:middle line:90%
So let's get into that.

00:15:42.170 --> 00:15:44.517 align:middle line:84%
So the first
question I was going

00:15:44.517 --> 00:15:45.600 align:middle line:90%
to ask you about all that.

00:15:45.600 --> 00:15:47.850 align:middle line:84%
Do you think there is
sufficient enough suffering

00:15:47.850 --> 00:15:51.595 align:middle line:84%
