00:15:51.595 --> 00:15:53.680 align:middle line:90%
>>ARNTZ: I think so.

00:15:53.680 --> 00:15:57.110 align:middle line:84%
And, in fact, I've
recently been getting calls

00:15:57.110 --> 00:15:59.840 align:middle line:84%
