are really suffering.

00:16:08.637 --> 00:16:10.595 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Yeah, they're
start-- it's starting.

00:16:10.595 --> 00:16:12.020 align:middle line:90%
>>ARNTZ: It's really happening.

00:16:12.020 --> 00:16:13.070 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Alcoholism.

00:16:13.070 --> 00:16:17.150 align:middle line:84%
